name: we were parasite
description: we drank what was left. after it dripped through unimaginably deep crevices. and down sagging flesh. pulling it closer to where it would eventually end up. we sipped what was left after it had cleaned. after it had caused empty orgasms. after it had briefly replenished. before stripping away. we lapped it up for salvation. with the hope that one day we'd drink from the source.
